Hetuduka
Upādinnattika
Pañhāvāra
Paccayānulomapaccanīya
Hetuduka
93.
2798Hetupaccayā naārammaṇe satta, naadhipatiyā satta, naanantare satta, nasamanantare satta, naaññamaññe cattāri, naupanissaye satta, napurejāte satta, napacchājāte satta, naāsevane satta, nakamme satta, navipāke cattāri, naāhāre satta, naindriye satta, najhāne satta, namagge satta, nasampayutte cattāri, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā satta, novigate satta.
